text: Liked they provide brown rice. Dishes are healthy and not oily (even the pork chop is not oily). Highly Recommended for those looking for healthy mixed veg brown rice in this neighbourhood!

I ordered the kungpao chicken.. the chicken taste like frozen chicken...

Portion not okay.. 2 vege and 1 meat.. $4sgd

The stall managed by a couple.. so the service very slow...

I would say healthy dishes but not that yummy.. maybe elderly like it because healthy dishes means not yummy food..
Was checking out what's the hype for the long queue of this cai fan stall. Their food is tasty and less oil. Had an awesome meal. Will definitely come again!
My boy bought rice with 2 prawns, sweet & sour pork and cabbage. Stall charged him $5.30. Explained that prawn cost $1 each while 1 meat & 1 veg is $3.30. Totally dishonest!
Iâ€™m regular customer, feel less oily compare to others, like their soup as well and healthy choice of brown rice available. Average price of $4 with 2vege+1meat depends what on what your order is.
